rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0001
rows.name: Commander—we located the Lifehold, but...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0002
rows.name: Yeah—Irina already briefed me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0003
rows.name: I'm just glad you all got back here safe 'n' sound.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0004
rows.name: Wish we could say the same for that Archive unit.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0005
rows.name: Another swath of Earth's legacy... It's irreplaceable.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0006
rows.name: Yeah, well, so are all of you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0007
rows.name: So cheer up, huh? C'mon, let's get you guys fed.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0008
rows.name: Dinner is on me this time.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0009
rows.name: Okay, this is weird.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0010
rows.name: Very weird.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0011
rows.name: Tatsu is suspicious![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0012
rows.name: What, a commander can't treat his troops?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0017
rows.name: If you're trying to thank us for this job, there's really no need.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0018
rows.name: This time it was Irina's team.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0019
rows.name:
Next time it could be my team;
any BLADE would do the same for us.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0020
rows.name: Okay, fair enough.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0021
rows.name: Besides, Linly cooks best![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0022
rows.name: Hey—thanks, Tatsu![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0023
rows.name: Just for that, I'll make you some dessert, today.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0024
rows.name: Oh-ho-ho-hooo![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0025
rows.name: There you go.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0026
rows.name: The spud's right—no one cooks like Lin.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0027
rows.name:
Thanks, Commander!
If you wanted to join us, maybe I could—[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0028
rows.name: Great, let's eat![ST:wait ]
